  "text": "As HUCBNP have been induced toward neuronal differentiation by CM and/or NGF 6 and IFN-g was reported to facilitate NGFinduced neuronal differentiation, [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] we investigated the combined effect of hrIFN-g and NGF on HUCBNP (Figure 7) . It is evident that the combined treatment, either at 7 or 14 days, induced a significant higher differentiation response compared with the effect of each individual factor.",
